## 10:11 AM — Dry Run Mode Added to Content Delivery

Brandon asked how to safely test before sending real emails. Added dry run mode:
- Toggle ON by default (yellow banner: 🧪 Dry Run Mode)
- Dry run: lists who would receive emails without actually sending
- Live mode: actually sends via Postmark
- Edge function updated to accept `dry_run: true` parameter
- Frontend deployed to gh-pages
- Edge function needs manual deploy: `npx supabase functions deploy gallery_delivery`
